\nc<>Today, I'm thinking of doing a casual chat stream with
everyone in the city!
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[7]The magical girl who protects the town");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[7]Is it okay to stream something like this?");

\nc<>It's really me, Levantia. Since there haven't been any
particular incidents today, I'm doing it in my free time.

\nc<>Hehe. Did you think you could get away with it? You're
banned. Take a minute to reflect!
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[7]No, how obsessed are you with Levantia?");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[7]That person also appears in other streams.");
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[7]Didnt we do that kind of stuff before?");

\nc<>Yes, then I will continue to stream in a pure manner~ If
you have anything on your mind, feel free to ask!
\nc<>(Chatting with the listeners, it might be surprisingly fun.)
\nc<>I obtained the memory of Levantia's live stream.
